```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  actor Operator
  participant App as App.svelte
  participant Confirm as AutoModeConfirmModal
  participant PS as ProgramScreen
  participant Backend as program_routes.rs
  participant PTW as PlanToWaves
  participant Parser as LasdlcPlanParser
  participant Assembler as CriteriaAssembler
  participant CGK as CanonGatekeeper<P>
  participant Shield as IndirectInjectionShield
  participant Supervisor as program_supervisor.rs
  participant SSE as SSE broadcast
  participant TaskStore as programTasks.ts

  Operator->>App: Alt-A (or click Auto-Mode chip)
  App->>App: autoMode.set(true) + localStorage persist

  Operator->>PS: Enter codenames + click Start
  PS->>PS: check $autoMode === true
  PS->>Confirm: show AutoModeConfirmModal (G6 PBGC HARD)
  Confirm->>Operator: list codenames + wave count estimate
  Operator->>Confirm: APPROVE

  Confirm->>Backend: POST /api/program/plan { codenames: ["foo", "bar"] }
  Note over Backend: AuthGuard → is_valid_codename() each
  loop per codename
    Backend->>Backend: resolve ~/.claude/plans/<codename>.md (ancestor-walk CWE-22)
    Backend->>Backend: tokio::fs::read_to_string
    Backend->>PTW: PlanToWaves::run(content, codename, provider, shield, cancel_token)
    PTW->>Parser: LasdlcPlanParser::parse(content)
    alt parse OK
      Parser-->>PTW: ParsedPlan { phases, shipped_means, ... }
      PTW->>Assembler: assemble(CriteriaSource::BuildPlanExcerpts + CanonExcerpts)
      Assembler-->>PTW: Criteria { entries }
      PTW->>CGK: critique(Draft{Plan, content}, criteria)
      CGK->>CGK: build_prompt(draft, criteria)
      CGK-->>CGK: LLM call (temperature=0)
      CGK-->>PTW: Verdict { status: Validated, findings }
      loop per PlanPhase × Wave × Task
        PTW->>Shield: scan(preamble + task_prompt)
        alt Clean
          Shield-->>PTW: ShieldOutcome::Clean
          PTW->>PTW: emit TaskSpec { prompt: "[codename/Phase/Wave/Task]\nGuarantees:...\n<prompt>" }
        else Flagged HIGH+
          Shield-->>PTW: ShieldOutcome::Flagged
          PTW->>PTW: skip TaskSpec; push gap warning
        end
      end
      PTW-->>Backend: PlanToWavesResult { builds: [ProgramBuildSpec], gaps }
    else parse Err (NotLasdlcCompliant etc.)
      Parser-->>PTW: Err(reason)
      PTW-->>Backend: PlanToWavesResult { builds: [ProgramBuildSpec{waves:[]}], gaps: [reason] }
    end
  end
  Backend-->>Confirm: 200 { builds: [...], warnings: [...] }
  Confirm->>PS: proceed with populated ProgramBuildSpec[]

  PS->>Supervisor: POST /api/program/start { builds: [...] }
  loop per build × wave × task
    Supervisor->>SSE: broadcast TaskStart { build_id, task_id, spec }
    SSE->>TaskStore: SSE event → programTasks.update(Map<build_id, TaskSpecView[]>)
    TaskStore->>TaskStore: WaveLive.svelte renders read-only chips
  end
  Supervisor-->>PS: 200 { program_id }
  Note over PS,TaskStore: Terminal never opened (P1 PBGC G5: terminal_window_open_count === 0)
```
